		<tr valign=top>
			<td class="BoardRowB" colspan=2 width="83%">
				I expect a lot of flame on this topic, but I feel it needs to be posted. <br>  <br> I have emailed SOE to make epic items pretty much all NO DROP - dragon scales first and foremost. Hopefully many of you other players will do the same. <br>  <br> You choice now as a warrior on E'ci is this; <br> +If you don't belong to a power guild chance of getting to Sev for a kill - zero. <br> +If you don't belong to a power guild chance of getting a no drop weap that compares or is better than epic - zero. <br> +How you can get a green scale - farm 60 to 100k to support this practice. <br> +I expect most wars will end up scraping forever and paying 10k for a snowchipper and/or 7k for a frosty. And then undergo harsh tells asking why they can't keep aggro at high end raids. <br>  <br> These are epic items. I realize dragons drop other items besides (sometimes) scales but to kill Sev every time he pops and then charge a fortune for an epic item is wrong.  <br>  <br> How about letting Sev be public like Vox and Nagafen? Is that too much to ask? Although I expect if vox and naggy weren't lvl restricted there would be no getting at them ahead of a power guild either. <br>  <br> And yes, I will laugh so hard if SOE makes scales no drop and your caster or mule has to destroy or MQ a scale. <br>  <br> Strikes, 51 Vah Shir Warrior <br> Wielding Jagged blade of mourning and Shimmering partisan <br>  <br> 
